Subject: FSAA Scan Performance
Description:
Team,

Our latest FSAA scan ran at 15 days and I'm wondering if there's a way to tweak the scan settings to increase the performance of the job. Any thoughts or recommendations?
Solution_Comment__c:
[Issue]
FSAA Scans taking 15+ days to complete

[Resolution]
We limited the probable owners scanned for from unlimited to 4, which should speed the scan up some, but ultimately we agreed we'd see a greater performance increase with upgrading to 11.6 and setting up a proxy
